## 权威声明 / Authority Statement

**【强制标准-001：最高效力 / Mandatory-001: Supreme Authority】**
本文档为企业产品研发领域的最高标准文件，所有工作必须严格遵守。
This document is the highest standard in the field of enterprise product R&D, and all work must strictly comply.

**【强制标准-002：违反后果 / Mandatory-002: Violation Consequences】**
违反L1强制标准 → 产出视为无效 → 必须整改 → 重新审查，无例外豁免。
Violating L1 Mandatory Standards → Output is invalid → Must rectify → Re-review, no exceptions.

**【强制标准-003：文件体系 / Mandatory-003: Document System】**
- L1 强制标准（本文档核心，不可撼动）/ L1 Mandatory Standards (Core of this document, inviolable)
- L2 标准（架构设计标准）/ L2 Standards (Architecture Design Standards)
- L3 规则（开发实施规则）/ L3 Rules (Development Implementation Rules)
- L4 规范（编码/测试/部署规范）/ L4 Specifications (Coding/Testing/Deployment Specifications)
- L5 推荐（最佳实践）/ L5 Recommended (Best Practices)
- L6 参考（术语/清单/背景）/ L6 Reference (Terminology/Checklists/Background)

