| Vercel AI | api_key | vercel.com/ai |
| Meta AI | api_key | ai.meta.com |
| Mistral AI | api_key | mistral.ai |
| OpenRouter | api_key, base_url | openrouter.ai |

← 来源 / Source：ECPAS v2.0 §五

### L6-003：16类基础服务能力矩阵 / 16 Foundation Services Capability Matrix

#### 第一梯队 — 必须建设 / Tier 1 — MUST Build

**A. UAM — 用户与账户服务 / User & Account Service**
能力 / Capabilities：账户注册/登录/会话Token/SSO/MFA/第三方OAuth/设备指纹
Account register/login/session Token/SSO/MFA/third-party OAuth/device fingerprint

**B. PAY — 支付与交易服务 / Payment & Transaction Service**
能力 / Capabilities：微信支付/支付宝/银联云闪付/数字人民币/PayPal/Stripe
WeChat Pay/Alipay/UnionPay QuickPass/Digital RMB/PayPal/Stripe

**C. SMS — 安全与合规服务 / Security & Compliance Service**
能力 / Capabilities：MFA多因素认证/RBAC权限管理/欺诈检测/审计日志/PCI-DSS合规
MFA/RBAC permission management/fraud detection/audit logs/PCI-DSS compliance

**D. CFG — 配置与开关服务 / Configuration & Switch Service**
能力 / Capabilities：多环境配置/命名空间隔离/版本管理/灰度发布/实时推送/敏感加密
Multi-environment config/namespace isolation/version management/gradual release/realtime push/sensitive encryption

#### 第二梯队 — 尽快建设 / Tier 2 — SHOULD Build

**E. NTF — 消息通知服务 / Notification Service**
能力 / Capabilities：短信/邮件/APP推送/站内信/模板管理/频率控制/智能路由
SMS/email/app push/in-app message/template management/rate control/smart routing

**F. DAT — 数据采集服务 / Data Acquisition Service**
能力 / Capabilities：前端SDK/后端SDK/App SDK/事件模型/数据校验/实时监控
Frontend SDK/backend SDK/app SDK/event model/data validation/realtime monitoring

**G. MED — 媒体处理服务 / Media Processing Service**
能力 / Capabilities：断点续传/图片处理（缩略/水印/格式转换）/视频转码/存储
Resumable upload/image processing (thumbnail/watermark/format conversion)/video transcoding/storage

**H. MKT — 营销优惠服务 / Marketing & Promotion Service**
能力 / Capabilities：优惠券/满减/折扣/叠加计算/预算管控/库存管理/活动管理
Coupons/quantity discounts/discounts/stacking calculation/budget control/inventory management/campaign management

**I. PIM — 积分会员服务 / Points & Membership Service**
能力 / Capabilities：积分账户/积分获取/积分消耗/会员等级/成长值/积分商城
Points account/points earning/points redemption/membership level/growth value/points mall

#### 第三梯队 — 按需建设 / Tier 3 — MAY Build

**J. MOD — 内容审核服务 / Content Moderation Service**
能力 / Capabilities：文本审核/图片审核/视频审核/违禁内容检测/精准率/召回率模式
Text moderation/image moderation/video moderation/prohibited content detection/precision/recall modes

**K. GMG — 用户增长服务 / Growth & Marketing Service**
能力 / Capabilities：邀请码/裂变/拼团/任务系统/A/B测试/防刷风控
Invite code/fission/team purchase/task system/A/B testing/anti-fraud risk control

**L. CSC — 客服工单服务 / Customer Service Ticket Service**
能力 / Capabilities：工单创建/处理/关闭/评价/FAQ问答/知识库/数据分析
Ticket create/process/close/rate/FAQ Q&A/knowledge base/data analysis

**M. SRS — 搜索推荐服务 / Search & Recommendation Service**
能力 / Capabilities：全文检索/语义搜索/高亮/纠错/个性化推荐/协同过滤
Full-text search/semantic search/highlight/correction/personalized recommendation/collaborative filtering

**N. CDN — 内容分发服务 / Content Delivery Service**
能力 / Capabilities：全球加速/HTTPS/防盗链/缓存策略/性能优化
Global acceleration/HTTPS/anti-hotlink/cache strategy/performance optimization

#### 第四梯队 — 长期规划 / Tier 4 — Long-term Planning

**O. INS — 分析洞察服务 / Insights & Analytics Service**
能力 / Capabilities：漏斗分析/留存分析/路径分析/归因分析/用户画像/报表看板
Funnel analysis/retention analysis/path analysis/attribution analysis/user profiling/report dashboard

**P. STR — 实时计算服务 / Streaming Service**
能力 / Capabilities：实时ETL/实时指标/实时风控/流批一体/Flink
Real-time ETL/real-time metrics/real-time risk control/unified stream-batch/Flink

**Q. OPS — 运营效率服务 / Operations Efficiency Service**
能力 / Capabilities：消息中心/弹窗管理/Banner管理/CMS内容管理/表单系统
Message center/popup management/banner management/CMS content management/form system

← 来源 / Source：ECGS §2.2 + 附录A完整能力矩阵 / Appendix A Complete Capability Matrix

### L6-004：基础服务依赖关系矩阵 / Foundation Services Dependency Matrix

| 被依赖\依赖 / Depended upon \ Depends on | UAM | PAY | SMS | NTF | MOD | CSC | MKT | PIM |
|----------------------------------------|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|-----|
| UAM (用户账户 / User Account) | - | | ★★ | ★ | | | | ★ |
| PAY (支付 / Payment) | ★★★ | - | ★★ | ★ | | ★ | ★★ | ★ |
| SMS (安全 / Security) | ★★ | ★★ | - | ★ | | | ★ | |
| NTF (消息通知 / Notification) | ★★ | ★ | | - | | ★ | ★ | ★ |
| MOD (内容审核 / Moderation) | ★ | | ★ | | - | | | |
| CSC (客服工单 / Customer Service) | ★★ | ★ | ★ | ★ | ★ | - | | ★ |
| MKT (营销优惠 / Marketing) | ★★ | ★★ | | ★ | | | - | ★★★ |
| PIM (积分会员 / Points & Membership) | ★★ | ★ | | ★ | | | ★★ | - |

**核心依赖解读 / Core dependency interpretation：**

1. UAM 是几乎所有服务的强依赖（用户身份是基础）/ UAM is a strong dependency for almost all services (user identity is fundamental)
2. PAY 依赖 UAM 和 SMS（支付必须知道谁付、是否安全）/ PAY depends on UAM and SMS (payment must know who pays and if it's secure)
3. MKT 和 PIM 互相强依赖（积分和优惠通常联动）/ MKT and PIM have strong mutual dependency (points and promotions usually linked)
4. GMG 依赖多个服务（增长是综合能力体现）/ GMG depends on multiple services (growth is a comprehensive capability)

← 来源 / Source：附录A §R

### L6-005：技术实现建议 / Technology Implementation Recommendations

**【自建 vs SaaS选型 / Build vs SaaS Selection】**

**建议自建（复用价值高+数据敏感）/ Recommended for self-build (high reuse value + data sensitive)：**
- UAM/PAY/SMS（数据必须自主可控 / Data must be self-controlled）
- MKT/PIM/GMG（业务核心know-how / Core business know-how）
- CFG（深度集成开关 / Deep integration switches）
- DAT（数据资产 / Data assets）

**可选SaaS（标准化程度高+接入成本低）/ Optional SaaS (high standardization + low integration cost)：**
- NTF（短信通道可采购阿里云/腾讯云 / SMS channel can use Alibaba Cloud/Tencent Cloud）
- MOD（内容审核可采购网易/数美 / Content moderation can use NetEase/Shumei）
- MED（媒体处理可采购阿里云视频云 / Media processing can use Alibaba Cloud Video）
- CDN（可采购阿里云CDN/腾讯云CDN / Can use Alibaba Cloud CDN/Tencent Cloud CDN）
- CSC（可采购Zendesk/Udesk / Can use Zendesk/Udesk）

**【技术栈建议 / Technology Stack Recommendations】**

- 后端框架 / Backend framework：Go(高性能/high performance)/Java Spring Boot(成熟/mature)/Python FastAPI
- 数据库 / Database：PostgreSQL(事务/transaction)/MySQL(业务/business)/Redis(缓存/cache)/ES(搜索/search)
- 消息队列 / Message queue：Kafka(事件/events)/RabbitMQ(任务/tasks)
- 缓存 / Cache：Redis Cluster
- 搜索 / Search：Elasticsearch(全文/full-text)/Meilisearch(轻量/lightweight)
- 文件存储 / File storage：MinIO(私有/on-prem)/OSS/S3
- 实时计算 / Real-time computing：Flink/Storm
- 报表 / Reporting：Apache Superset / Metabase

← 来源 / Source：附录A §T

